pageContext.claim: “'Seems like the Department of Justice (and FBI) had a program to keep Donald Trump from becoming President'”. @DarrellIssa  @foxandfriends  If this had happened to the other side, everybody involved would be in jail. This is a Media coverup of the biggest story of our time.”
pageContext.analysis: There is no evidence that the Justice Department had a program to prevent Trump from becoming president. The FBI letter on the reopening of the email investigation against Hillary Clinton likely tipped the election narrowly to Trump.
